掉转车头  做好紧急疏散的准备
Turn the cars! Ready for emergency evacuation.

2053
01:51:55,980 --> 01:51:58,890
...焊工镜片  各就各位
...welder's glass. Everybody take their places.

2054
01:51:59,190 --> 01:52:01,230
每人都拿一个焊工镜片
Everybody take a welder's glass!

2055
01:52:56,210 --> 01:52:57,320
20分钟
20 minutes.

2056
01:53:01,550 --> 01:53:02,700
20分钟
20 minutes!

2057
01:53:13,970 --> 01:53:15,050
20分钟
That's 20!

2058
01:53:18,730 --> 01:53:19,930
放我腿上谢谢
On the leg, please.

2059
01:53:21,400 --> 01:53:23,310
-费曼  -不用了
- Feynman? - No.

2060
01:53:23,730 --> 01:53:26,060
车玻璃能阻挡紫外线
The glass stops the UV.

2061
01:53:26,240 --> 01:53:27,650
要是玻璃碎了可怎么办呢
What stops the glass?

2062
01:53:29,240 --> 01:53:30,690
我去大本营了
I'm heading to base camp.

2063
01:53:30,750 --> 01:53:31,870
祝你好运
Best of luck.

2064
01:53:32,630 --> 01:53:33,580
罗伯特
Robert?

2065
01:53:35,260 --> 01:53:36,660
尽量别把世界给炸了
Try not to blow up the world.

2066
01:53:48,810 --> 01:53:49,940
盯住那个指针
Watch that needle.

2067
01:53:49,940 --> 01:53:51,400
如果引爆装置没充电
If the detonators don't charge,

2068
01:53:51,400 --> 01:53:53,270
电压掉到一伏以下
and the voltage drops below one volt,

2069
01:53:53,280 --> 01:53:56,560
就按那个按钮中止  明白了吗
you hit that button, you abort. Understood?

2070
01:53:56,740 --> 01:53:57,810
明白了
Understood.

2071
01:54:05,200 --> 01:54:07,490
两分钟后引爆
Two minutes to detonation.

2072
01:54:07,620 --> 01:54:08,870
全体趴下
Everybody down!

2073
01:54:09,670 --> 01:54:12,950
看到山上反光之前不要转身
Do not turn around until you see light reflected on the hills.

2074
01:54:13,750 --> 01:54:16,550
然后只能通过焊工镜片观察爆炸
Then look at the explosion only through your welder's glass.

2075
01:54:16,550 --> 01:54:19,630
90秒后引爆
90 seconds to detonation.

2076
01:54:20,930 --> 01:54:23,760
80秒后引爆
80 seconds to detonation.

2077
01:54:24,090 --> 01:54:25,380
搽上了吗
Is it rubbed in?

2078
01:54:26,180 --> 01:54:27,090
是的
Yeah.

2079
01:54:33,940 --> 01:54:37,010
60秒后引爆
60 seconds to detonation.

2080
01:54:51,500 --> 01:54:53,780
这些事让人揪心
These things are hard on your heart.

2081
01:54:53,960 --> 01:54:55,090
30秒
30 seconds.

2082
01:55:00,590 --> 01:55:02,210
引爆装置充电完毕
Detonators charged!

2083
01:55:12,230 --> 01:55:13,600
17.

2084
01:55:13,730 --> 01:55:15,190
16.

2085
01:55:15,190 --> 01:55:16,770
15.

2086
01:55:16,980 --> 01:55:18,390
14.

2087
01:55:18,820 --> 01:55:20,270
13.

2088
01:55:20,650 --> 01:55:21,730
12.

2089
01:55:22,200 --> 01:55:23,190
11.

2090
01:55:23,870 --> 01:55:24,900
Ten.

2091
01:55:26,200 --> 01:55:27,070
Nine.

2092
01:55:28,080 --> 01:55:29,120
Eight.

2093
01:55:30,410 --> 01:55:31,410
Seven.

2094
01:55:32,960 --> 01:55:33,950
Six.

2095
01:55:35,830 --> 01:55:36,790
Five.

2096
01:55:38,380 --> 01:55:39,290
Four.

2097
01:55:41,050 --> 01:55:41,870
Three.

2098
01:55:43,470 --> 01:55:44,540
Two.

2099
01:55:46,100 --> 01:55:46,610
One.

2100
01:57:19,980 --> 01:57:22,220
"如今  我已成为死神"
"And now I am become Death...

2101
01:57:24,740 --> 01:57:26,690
"世界的毁灭者"
the destroyer of worlds."

2102
01:57:59,930 --> 01:58:01,100
成功了
It worked.

2103
01:58:36,640 --> 01:58:38,220
你欠我十美元
You owe me ten dollars!

2104
01:58:40,730 --> 01:58:43,970
-快拿来  -我愿赌服输  基斯蒂
- Come on! - I... I'm good for it, Kisti.

2105
01:58:44,350 --> 01:58:45,220
确实
You are!

2106
01:58:46,280 --> 01:58:47,770
是的  你确实
Yes, you are!

2107
01:59:25,100 --> 01:59:26,890
立刻给我接波茨坦
Get me Potsdam right away.

2108
01:59:38,250 --> 01:59:39,730
捎个信给吉蒂
Get a message to Kitty.

2109
01:59:40,160 --> 01:59:42,910
-我们什么都不能说  -告诉她收床单
- We can't say anything. - Tell her to take in the sheets.

2110
01:59:58,140 --> 01:59:59,890
-喂  -喂  吉蒂吗
- Hello? - Hi, Kitty?

2111
01:59:59,890 --> 02:00:03,470
什么什么  夏洛特  你说你说
What? What? Charlotte? Charlotte, go ahead. Go ahead.

2112
02:00:03,770 --> 02:00:04,680
我不太清楚
Well, I don't know,

2113
02:00:04,690 --> 02:00:07,560
他就告诉我让你收床单
he just said to tell you to bring in the sheets.

2114
02:00:10,280 --> 02:00:11,060
吉蒂
Kitty?

2115
02:00:12,950 --> 02:00:15,690
吉蒂  吉蒂你还在听吗
Kitty? Kitty, are you still there?

2116
02:00:22,800 --> 02:00:24,250
如果在过高的空中引爆
If they detonate it too high in the air,

2117
02:00:24,250 --> 02:00:26,040
爆炸威力不会这么强
the blast won't be as powerful.

2118
02:00:26,040 --> 02:00:29,830
恕我直言  奥本海默博士  接下来就由我们负责了
With respect, Dr. Oppenheimer, we'll take it from here.

2119
02:00:40,220 --> 02:00:42,920
杜鲁门在波茨坦跟斯大林通气了吗
Did Truman brief Stalin at Potsdam?

2120
02:00:43,320 --> 02:00:45,640
"通气"有点夸张了
"Brief" would be an overstatement.

2121
02:00:45,640 --> 02:00:49,770
他提到了一种颇具威力的新型武器
He referred to a powerful new weapon.

2122
02:00:50,020 --> 02:00:55,270
斯大林...希望我们用它对付日本
Stalin... hoped we'd use it against Japan.

2123
02:00:56,190 --> 02:00:57,060
就这样吗
That's it?

2124
02:00:57,870 --> 02:00:59,780
罗伯特  我们已经给了他们王牌
Robert, we've given them an ace.

2125
02:00:59,780 --> 02:01:01,490
打牌的是他们
It's for them to play the hand.

2126
02:01:03,490 --> 02:01:04,900
你打算6号用吗
You're aiming for the sixth?

2127
02:01:05,660 --> 02:01:07,950
这取决于太平洋司令
It's up to the CO in the Pacific.

2128
02:01:09,340 --> 02:01:11,080
要我和你一起去华盛顿吗
Should I come with you to Washington?

2129
02:01:12,670 --> 02:01:13,580
去做什么
What for?

2130
02:01:16,350 --> 02:01:17,880
那你有消息随时告诉我
Well, you keep me informed.

2131
02:01:19,350 --> 02:01:20,210
当然
Of course.

2132
02:01:22,510 --> 02:01:23,670
尽我所能
As best I can.

2133
02:01:41,910 --> 02:01:44,570
日本人如果知道接下来发生的事会投降吗
Would the Japanese surrender if they knew what was coming?

2134
02:01:45,830 --> 02:01:46,960
我不清楚
I don't know.

2135
02:01:49,720 --> 02:01:51,620
你看过西拉德的请愿书吗
Have you seen Szilard's petition?

2136
02:01:51,780 --> 02:01:54,120
西拉德怎么可能了解日本人
How the hell does Szilard know about the Japanese?

2137
02:01:54,550 --> 02:01:55,960
你不打算签吧
You're not signing it, are you?

2138
02:01:56,670 --> 02:01:59,000
很多人签了  许多
Many people have. A lot of people.

2139
02:01:59,050 --> 02:02:00,040
爱德华...
Edward...

2140
02:02:01,680 --> 02:02:04,470
我们是造了这枚炸弹  但这并没有赋予我们
the fact that we built this bomb does not give us any more,

2141
02:02:04,470 --> 02:02:06,350
任何多于常人的权利或责任
any more right or responsibility

2142
02:02:06,350 --> 02:02:08,850
来决定如何使用它
to decide how it's used than anyone else.

2143
02:02:08,850 --> 02:02:10,850
但我们是唯一知道它的人
But we're the only people who know about it.

2144
02:02:11,150 --> 02:02:14,190
我把学术界的各种声音告诉过史汀生
I've told Stimson the various opinions of the community.

2145
02:02:14,190 --> 02:02:15,570
但你怎么说
But what's your opinion?

2146
02:02:16,780 --> 02:02:18,060
一旦使用...
Once it's used...

2147
02:02:19,400 --> 02:02:21,690
核战争  也许...
nuclear war, perhaps...

2148
02:02:21,910 --> 02:02:23,070
所有战争...
all war...

2149
02:02:24,660 --> 02:02:25,980
变得难以想象
becomes unthinkable.

2150
02:02:26,580 --> 02:02:28,700
直到有人造出更大的
Until somebody builds a bigger one.

2151
02:02:49,730 --> 02:02:51,270
我以为他们会打电话
I thought they would call.

2152
02:02:51,270 --> 02:02:53,010
这才5号
It's only the fifth.

2153
02:02:55,440 --> 02:02:57,310
在日本  是6号了
In Japan, it's the sixth.

2154
02:03:10,080 --> 02:03:10,990
夏洛特
Charlotte?

2155
02:03:13,670 --> 02:03:14,700
打给格罗夫斯试试
Try Groves.

2156
02:03:16,210 --> 02:03:17,250
有消息吗
Anything?

2157
02:03:19,630 --> 02:03:22,290
-夏洛特  -杜鲁门在广播
- Charlotte? - Truman's on the radio.

2158
02:03:23,510 --> 02:03:26,040
16小时前
16 hours ago,

2159
02:03:26,340 --> 02:03:28,300
一架美国战机
an American airplane

2160
02:03:28,510 --> 02:03:31,930
在广岛投下一枚炸弹
dropped one bomb on Hiroshima,

2161
02:03:33,190 --> 02:03:36,600
彻底摧毁了这座城市的军工生产能力
and destroyed its usefulness to the enemy.

2162
02:03:38,440 --> 02:03:40,810
这枚炸弹的威力
The bomb has more power

2163
02:03:40,860 --> 02:03:44,270
超过两万吨TNT
than 20,000 tons of TNT.

2164
02:03:46,410 --> 02:03:48,490
这是一枚原子弹
It is an atomic bomb.

2165
02:03:51,120 --> 02:03:55,950
这是对宇宙基本力量的运用
It is a harnessing of the basic power of the universe.

2166
02:03:58,090 --> 02:03:59,290
格罗夫斯在一号线
Groves on one.

2167
02:04:05,340 --> 02:04:06,250
将军
General?

2168
02:04:06,380 --> 02:04:09,170
我为你感到非常骄傲  为你领导的所有人
I'm very proud of you, and all of your people.

2169
02:04:09,350 --> 02:04:10,500
一切顺利吗
It went alright?

2170
02:04:10,890 --> 02:04:13,510
据说是一次爆炸式的成功
Apparently it went with a tremendous bang.

2171
02:04:14,390 --> 02:04:18,600
为此这里每个人都相当高兴
Well, everyone here is feeling reasonably good about it.

2172
02:04:20,110 --> 02:04:21,730
这一路过来不容易
It's been a long road.

2173
02:04:21,740 --> 02:04:23,910
我认为我做过最明智的事
I think one of the wisest things I ever did

2174
02:04:23,910 --> 02:04:26,820
就是选了你当洛斯阿拉莫斯的负责人
was when I selected the director of Los Alamos.

2175
02:04:29,870 --> 02:04:33,860
我们花了这二十多亿美元
We have spent more than two billion dollars

2176
02:04:33,920 --> 02:04:37,990
全押在历史上最大的科学赌博上
on the greatest scientific gamble in history,

2177
02:04:38,170 --> 02:04:40,370
然后我们赢了
and we have won.

2178
02:04:44,760 --> 02:05:01,220
奥比  奥比  奥比
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

2179
02:06:08,350 --> 02:06:09,580
全世界...
The world...

2180
02:06:11,510 --> 02:06:13,250
将铭记这一天
will remember this day.

2181
02:06:31,870 --> 02:06:33,480
现在还无法
It's too soon to...

2182
02:06:34,280 --> 02:06:36,000
现在还无法确定
It's too soon to determine

2183
02:06:36,000 --> 02:06:38,320
投弹的最终结果
what the results of the bombing are.

2184
02:06:41,290 --> 02:06:43,490
不过我敢打赌  日本人肯定受罪了
But I'll bet the Japanese didn't like it.

2185
02:07:03,710 --> 02:07:05,220
我非常自豪
I'm so proud.

2186
02:07:06,440 --> 02:07:08,520
为你们的成就而自豪
So proud of what you have accomplished.

2187
02:07:16,060 --> 02:07:19,110
可惜当时没来得及用它对付德国人
I just wish we had it in time to use against the Germans.

2188
02:09:08,540 --> 02:09:09,760
奥本海默博士
Dr. Oppenheimer?

2189
02:09:10,940 --> 02:09:12,140
奥本海默博士
Dr. Oppenheimer?

2190
02:09:13,240 --> 02:09:14,350
照片不错
Nice picture.

2191
02:09:15,120 --> 02:09:16,770
杜鲁门总统可以见你了
President Truman will see you now.

2192
02:09:31,170 --> 02:09:34,000
奥本海默博士  幸会
Dr. Oppenheimer, it's an honor.

2193
02:09:34,000 --> 02:09:35,960
-总统先生  -请坐
- Mr. President. - Please.

2194
02:09:35,960 --> 02:09:36,960
谢谢
Thank you.

2195
02:09:37,630 --> 02:09:39,080
伯恩斯部长
Secretary Byrnes.

2196
02:09:41,560 --> 02:09:44,960
成为全世界最有名的人  感觉怎么样
How's it feel to be the most famous man in the world?

2197
02:09:45,470 --> 02:09:48,640
你拯救了很多美国人的生命
You helped save a lot of American lives.

2198
02:09:48,730 --> 02:09:53,020
-我们在广岛的行动...  -还有长崎
- What we did at Hiroshima was... - And Nagasaki.

2199
02:09:53,820 --> 02:09:55,520
当然
Obviously.

2200
02:09:56,030 --> 02:09:59,070
因为你的发明  我们的士兵才安全归来了
Your invention let us bring our boys home.

2201
02:09:59,070 --> 02:10:02,700
不能说是我的发明
Well, it was hardly... my invention.

2202
02:10:02,700 --> 02:10:05,030
《时代》封面上的人是你
It was you on the cover of Time.

2203
02:10:07,600 --> 02:10:11,460
吉姆说  你担心我们和苏联展开军备竞赛
Jim tells me you're concerned about an arms race with the Soviets.

2204
02:10:11,460 --> 02:10:12,700
是的
Ah, yes, ah...

2205
02:10:14,040 --> 02:10:15,120
这个...
Well, um...

2206
02:10:15,630 --> 02:10:20,040
现在是时候
it's that, uh, now is our chance to secure...

2207
02:10:20,890 --> 02:10:23,720
就原子能开展国际合作了
international cooperation on atomic energy,

2208
02:10:23,720 --> 02:10:25,970
我担心
and-and-and I'm concerned...

2209
02:10:25,970 --> 02:10:29,100
你知道苏联什么时候能拥有原子弹吗
Do you know when the Soviets are gonna have the bomb?

2210
02:10:29,230 --> 02:10:30,730
我没法给出准确的...
I don't think I could give a...

2211
02:10:30,730 --> 02:10:31,760
永不
Never!

2212
02:10:32,980 --> 02:10:33,890
永不
Never.

2213
02:10:34,820 --> 02:10:38,070
总统先生  苏联拥有优秀的物理学家
Mr. President, the Russians have good physicists,

2214
02:10:38,070 --> 02:10:40,780
-和丰富的资源  -还"丰富的"
- and, and abundant resources... - Abundant?

2215
02:10:40,780 --> 02:10:41,610
没错
Yes.

2216
02:10:42,410 --> 02:10:44,360
我不这么想
I don't think so.

2217
02:10:44,530 --> 02:10:48,190
他们会倾尽全力...
Well, they'll put everything they have in...

2218
02:10:51,750 --> 02:10:55,790
听说你要离开洛斯阿拉莫斯
I hear you're leaving Los Alamos.

2219
02:10:56,710 --> 02:10:58,210
该怎么处理它呢
What should we do with it?

2220
02:10:58,340 --> 02:11:00,040
还给原住民
Give it back to the Indians.

2221
02:11:09,060 --> 02:11:10,630
奥本海默博士
Dr. Oppenheimer...

2222
02:11:11,270 --> 02:11:14,220
如果你对苏联人的判断是对的
if what you say about the Soviets is true,

2223
02:11:14,440 --> 02:11:18,850
我们必须扩建实验室  而不是把它关掉
we have to build up Los Alamos, not shut it down.

2224
02:11:22,240 --> 02:11:23,690
总统先生
Mr. President...

2225
02:11:29,250 --> 02:11:33,030
我感觉自己的手上沾满鲜血
I feel that I have blood on my hands.

2226
02:11:52,680 --> 02:11:56,220
你以为广岛
You think anyone in Hiroshima, or...

2227
02:11:56,810 --> 02:12:01,310
或长崎有人在乎原子弹是谁造的吗
Nagasaki, gives a shit who built the bomb?

2228
02:12:04,450 --> 02:12:06,560
他们在乎的是投弹的人
They care who dropped it.

2229
02:12:07,450 --> 02:12:08,650
是我
I did.

2230
02:12:11,300 --> 02:12:13,780
广岛与你无关
Hiroshima isn't about you.

2231
02:12:20,170 --> 02:12:22,040
奥本海默博士
Dr. Oppenheimer.

2232
02:12:33,060 --> 02:12:35,720
别再让那个爱哭鬼来了
Don't let that crybaby back in here!

2233
02:12:41,030 --> 02:12:44,400
罗伯特明白了  内疚根本没用
Robert saw that hand-wringing got him nowhere.

2234
02:12:44,950 --> 02:12:46,450
当我见到他时
By the time I met him,

2235
02:12:46,450 --> 02:12:49,610
他已经完全接受了"原子弹之父"的声誉
he'd fully embraced his "Father of the Bomb" reputation

2236
02:12:50,120 --> 02:12:53,110
并利用自己的身份影响政策
and used his profile to influence policy.

2237
02:13:01,630 --> 02:13:03,300
博士  战后几年
Doctor, in the years following the war,

2238
02:13:03,300 --> 02:13:05,510
你是否对美国的原子能政策
would you say that you exerted a great influence

2239
02:13:05,510 --> 02:13:07,390
施加了重大影响
on the atomic policies of the USA?

2240
02:13:07,390 --> 02:13:09,840
"重大"有点夸张了
I think "great" would be an overstatement.

2241
02:13:09,850 --> 02:13:12,060
是吗  就说说同位素问题吧
Really? I mean, look at the issue of isotopes.

2242
02:13:12,060 --> 02:13:13,720
不正是你本人
Were you not personally responsible for

